title: Community Collab | DeLUX Jam (LuxMix)

embed.description: Domics and Jomm took Lux's voice and remixed it. A double rainbow? What does it mean?! Domics: http://www.youtube.com/user/d0mics Jomm http://www.youtube.com/user/flashj0mm Additional Lux VO by LilyPichu https://www.youtube.com/user/LilyPichu **Created in collaboration with Riot Games**

body:
[Domics](https://www.youtube.com/user/d0mics) e [Jomm](https://www.youtube.com/user/flashj0mm) hanno preso la voce di Lux e l'hanno remixata.
Doppio arcobaleno? Ma cosa vuoi dire?

Frasi aggiuntive {{champion:99}} : [LilyPichu](https://www.youtube.com/user/LilyPichu)
